#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Lieutenant Skat (from German <foreignphrase lang=\"de\">Offiziersskat</"
#| "foreignphrase>) is a fun and engaging card game for two players, where "
#| "the second player is either live opponent, or built in artificial "
#| "intelligence."
msgid ""
"<literal>Lieutenant Skat</literal> (from German <foreignphrase lang=\"de"
"\">Offiziersskat</foreignphrase>) is a fun and engaging card game for two "
"players, where the second player is either live opponent, or built in "
"artificial intelligence."
msgstr ""
"Poručnik Skat (iz Njemačke <foreignphrase lang=\"de\">Offiziersskat</"
"foreignphrase>) je zabavna i privlačna igra za dva igrača, gdje je drugi "
"igrač ili živi protivnik, ili izgrađen kompjuterski."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game is played using a single deck of cards. Cards are shuffled and "
"distributed amongst the players in such a way that half of them are face "
"down and half of them are open. Each participant plays one of the open cards "
"per turn. As soon as all the cards are played the round ends and points are "
"calculated and awarded."
msgstr ""
"Igra se igra sa jednim špilom karata. Karte su poredane kod igrača na način "
"da se pola karata nalazi okrenuto ka dole, a pola karata je otvoreno. Svaki "
"igrač igra sa jednom otvorenom kartom u svakom krugu. Čim se sve karte "
"okrenu, obračunava se i pobjednik biva nagrađen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati?"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Objektivno:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Score more than 60 points in a single game."
msgstr "Osovoji više od šezdeset poena u jednoj igru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Once dealing is finished each player ends up with 16 cards each. Cards "
#| "are displayed in two horizontal rows - four cards per row. Half of the "
#| "cards are face down and half are face up. As a player you can see the "
#| "cards of your opponent as well as your own. You can make a move then by "
#| "clicking on any of your cards which are currently face up. The opponent "
#| "has to reply by choosing a corresponding card form his/her own stack. "
#| "<note><title>Note</title><para>If your opponent is artificial "
#| "intelligence, its cards will be chosen automatically.</para></note> Once "
#| "the exchange is finished values of the played cards are evaluated and "
#| "either you or your opponent is awarded points. The game is complete in 16 "
#| "rounds (when all of your and your opponent's cards have been played). "
#| "After the game ends your score is being compared to that of your opponent "
#| "and the player with the higher score wins the round."
msgid ""
"Once dealing is finished each player ends up with 16 cards each. Cards are "
"displayed in two horizontal rows - four cards per row. Half of the cards are "
"face down and half are face up. As a player you can see the cards of your "
"opponent as well as your own. You can make a move then by clicking on any of "
"your cards which are currently face up. The opponent has to reply by "
"choosing a corresponding card form his/her own stack."
msgstr ""
"Kada se završi dijeljenje svakom igraču ide 16 karti. Karte se prikazuju u "
"dva horizontalna reda - četiri kartice po redu. Polovina karti su licem "
"prema dolje, a pola su licem na gore. Kao igrač možete vidjeti kartice svog "
"protivnika i svoje karte. Možete napraviti potez, zatim klikom na bilo koju "
"od svojih karti koje su trenutno u opticaju. Protivnik ima da odgovori "
"odabirom odgovarajuće karte koje čine njegov / njen stack. <note> <title> "
"Napomena </title> <para> Ako je vaš protivnik računar, svoje kartice će biti "
"automatski izabrane. </para> </note> Nakon razmjene, vrijednosti karti se "
"ocjenjuju i bilo vi ili vaš protivnik je nagrađen poenima. Igra je završena "
"u 16 rundi (kada su sve vaše karte i  karte vašeg protivnika odigrane). "
"Nakon što je igra završena igrač sa višim rezultatom osvaja krug."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your opponent is artificial intelligence, its cards will be chosen "
"automatically."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the exchange is finished values of the played cards are evaluated and "
"either you or your opponent is awarded points. The game is complete in 16 "
"rounds (when all of your and your opponent's cards have been played). After "
"the game ends your score is being compared to that of your opponent and the "
"player with the higher score wins the round."
msgstr ""

