#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
#| "cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards "
#| "that are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of "
#| "those cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the "
#| "same suit, he can play with any other card including a 'trump' card."
msgid ""
"When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
"cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards that "
"are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of those "
"cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the same suit, "
"he can play with any other card including a <quote>trump</quote> card."
msgstr ""
"Kada igra počne, prvi igrač treba igrati sa bilo kojom kartom okrenutom ka "
"gore iz svoje hrpe. Ako drugi igrač trenutno ima neku kartu koja  je ista "
"kao karta od prvog igrača, a okrenuta je ka gore, mora da odgovori sa tom "
"kartom. Ako to nije slučaj, onda može igrati sa nekom drugom kartom "
"uključujući 'adut'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If there is at least one 'trump' card, the highest 'trump' wins both "
#| "cards."
msgid ""
"If there is at least one <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest "
"<quote>trump</quote> wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Ako se tu nalazi barem jedna adut karta, onda najveća adut karta osvaja obe "
"karte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If there is no 'trump' card, the highest card of the suit played by the "
#| "starting player wins both cards."
msgid ""
"If there is no <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest card of the suit "
"played by the starting player wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Ako nema karte koja je adut, onda najveća karta koju odigra igrač osvaja "
"obje karte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no 'trump' "
#| "card, he has to play any card and the starting player wins both cards."
msgid ""
"If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no "
"<quote>trump</quote> card, he has to play any card and the starting player "
"wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Ako igrač nema traženu kartu i nema kartu  'adut', mora da igra sam svim "
"kartama i igrač koji je počeo osvaja obe karte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The player who wins the round leads the next one."
msgstr "Pobjednik runde vodi za jedan."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Česta pitanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I play with a different deck of cards?"
msgstr "Mogu li promijeniti špil karata?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Refer to <link linkend=\"deck_change\">this</link> section of "
"'Interface Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Da. Idi na <link linkend=\"deck_change\">ovo</link> dio pregleda interfejsa "
"- 'Interface Overview' za još detalja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Napravio sam pogrešku. Da li je mogu poništiti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Ova igra nema <quote>Poništi</quote> opciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Da li mogu koristiti tastaturu za igru?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. ova igra se ne može igrati koristeći tastaturu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne mogu shvatiti što raditi ovdje. Da li mogu pronaći savjet?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Ova igra nema <quote>Hint</quote> opciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Želim izaći iz igrice, ali nisam još dovršio igru. Mogu li spasiti započeto?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Save State</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Ova igra nema <quote>Snimiti</quote> opciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change players' names?"
msgstr "Da li je moguće promijeniti imena igrača?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the names displayed on the right hand side of the game screen "
"refer to <link linkend=\"name_change\">this</link> section of 'Interface "
"Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Da, za promjenu imena ispisanih na desnoj strani ekrana idite na link <link "
"linkend=\"name_change\">ovo</link> dio preglednika interfejsa za detalje."

